\n26: \n27: ---\n28: \n29: ## Phase 3: TTL and Expiration\n30: \n31: - [ ] **3.1** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` - Add TTL check logic\n32: - [ ] **3.2** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` - Add idle timeout detection\n33: - [ ] **3.3** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` - Add MaxLifetime enforcement\n34: - [ ] **3.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/expiration.go` - isExpired() helper for TTL/Idle/MaxLifetime checks\n35: - [ ] **3.5** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/defaults.go` - Add DefaultTTL, DefaultIdleTimeout, DefaultMaxLifetime constants\n36: \n37: ---\n38: \n39: ## Phase 4: Batch Operations\n40: \n41: - [ ] **4.1** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers.go` - Add handleDeleteAllSandboxes() for namespace-wide deletion\n42: - [ ] **4.2** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers.go` - Add handleDeleteByLabelSelector() for filtered deletion\n43: - [ ] **4.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/batch_delete.go` - deleteStaleSandboxes() for Unknown/Failed state cleanup\n44: - [ ] **4.4** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/server.go` - Register DELETE /v1/namespaces/{ns}/sandboxes with query params\n45: \n46: ---\n47: \n48: ## Phase 5: Lifecycle Events and Webhooks\n49: \n50: - [ ] **5.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_events.go` - emitDeletionEvent() using event recorder\n51: - [ ] **5.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_events.go` - sendDeletionWebhook() with retry logic\n52: - [ ] **5.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_events.go` - logDeletionAudit() for audit trail\n53: - [ ] **5.4** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go` - Add WebhookConfig, AuditLogEntry types\n54: \n55: ---\n56: \n57: ## Phase 6: Resource Cleanup\n58: \n59: - [ ] **6.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/resource_cleanup.go` - cleanupServices() to delete owned Services\n60: - [ ] **6.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/resource_cleanup.go` - cleanupConfigMaps() to delete owned ConfigMaps\n61: - [ ] **6.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/resource_cleanup.go` - cleanupPVCs() with ReclaimPolicy handling\n62: - [ ] **6.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/resource_cleanup.go` - cleanupOrphanedResources() for external deletions\n63: \n64: ---\n65: \n66: ## Phase 7: Error Handling\n67: \n68: - [ ] **7.1** Update error types in `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go` - Add ErrSandboxNotFound, ErrDeletionFailed, ErrStaleFinalizer\n69: - [ ] **7.2** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers.go` - Map error types to HTTP status codes\n70: - [ ] **7.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/retry.go` - retryDeletion() with exponential backoff\n71: - [ ] **7.4** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go` - Add retry logic for failed deletions\n72: \n73: ---\n74: \n75: ## Phase 8: Integration with AR-005\n76: \n77: - [ ] **8.1** Integrate with sandbox_creator: Handle cleanup on creation failure (rollback)\n78: - [ ] **8.2** Integrate with store: Call DeleteSandbox(), GetSandbox() for deletion verification\n79: - [ ] **8.3** Integrate with k8s_client: Use dynamic client for deletion operations\n80: - [ ] **8.4** Ensure graceful shutdown integrates with existing informer watches\n81: \n82: ---\n83: \n84: ## Phase 9: Unit Tests\n85: \n86: - [ ] **9.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers_delete_test.go` - TestHandleSandboxDelete_Success\n87: - [ ] **9.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers_delete_test.go` - TestHandleSandboxDelete_NotFound\n88: - [ ] **9.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers_delete_test.go` - TestHandleSandboxDelete_Force\n89: - [ ] **9.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/graceful_shutdown_test.go` - TestDrainConnections\n90: - [ ] **9.5** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/graceful_shutdown_test.go` - TestExecutePreDeleteHook\n91: - [ ] **9.6** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go` - TestTTLExpiration\n92: - [ ] **9.7** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go` - TestIdleTimeout\n93: - [ ] **9.8** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/batch_delete_test.go` - TestDeleteAllInNamespace\n94: - [ ] **9.9** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/batch_delete_test.go` - TestDeleteByLabelSelector\n95: - [ ] **9.10** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/lifecycle_events_test.go` - TestEmitDeletionEvent\n96: - [ ] **9.11** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/resource_cleanup_test.go` - TestCleanupServices\n97: - [ ] **9.12** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/expiration_test.go` - TestIsExpired_TTL\n98: - [ ] **9.13** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/expiration_test.go` - TestIsExpired_IdleTimeout\n99: \n100: ---\n101: \n102: ## Phase 10: Integration Tests\n103: \n104: - [ ] **10.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/integration_delete_test.go` - E2E test for sandbox deletion\n105: - [ ] **10.2** Test graceful shutdown with active connections\n106: - [ ] **10.3** Test TTL expiration and cleanup\n107: - [ ] **10.4** Test batch deletion with 100+ sandboxes\n108: \n109: ---\n110: \n111: ## Phase 11: Verification\n112: \n113: - [ ] **11.1** Run `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - successful compilation\n114: - [ ] **11.2** Run `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - all unit tests pass\n115: - [ ] **11.3** Run `go test -race ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - no race conditions\n116: - [ ] **11.4** Run `go vet ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - no issues\n117: - [ ] **11.5** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` - linter passes\n118: - [ ] **11.6** Verify test coverage > 40% with `go test -coverprofile=coverage.out ./pkg/workloadmanager/...`\n119: \n120: ---\n121: \n122: ## Dependencies\n123: \n124: | Task | Depends On |\n125: |------|------------|\n126: | Phase 1 | AR-005 (Sandbox 创建处理器) |\n127: | Phase 2 | Phase 1 (handlers) |\n128: | Phase 3 | Phase 1 (handlers) |\n129: | Phase 4 | Phase 1-3 |\n130: | Phase 5 | Phase 1 (handlers) |\n131: | Phase 6 | AR-005 (k8s_client, informers) |\n132: | Phase 7 | Phase 1 (types) |\n133: | Phase 8 | AR-005 (sandbox_creator, store, k8s_client) |\n134: | Phase 9 | Phase 1-8 (implementation complete) |\n135: | Phase 10 | Phase 9 (unit tests) |\n136: | Phase 11 | All phases |\n137: \n138: ---\n139: \n140: ## References\n141: \n142: - Design: `sandbox-orchestration/AR-006-sandbox-deletion-lifecycle/design.md`\n143: - Delta Spec: `changes/AR-006/delta-spec.md`\n144: - Related AR: AR-005 (Sandbox 创建处理器)\n\n(End of file - total 144 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/workloadmanager  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-1 (Draft)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Deletion Handlers\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers.go` - Add handleSandboxDelete() handler for DELETE by SessionID\n- [ ] **1.2** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/handlers.go` - Add handleSandboxDeleteByName() handler for DELETE by name\n- [ ] **1.3** Update `pkg/workloadmanager/server.go` - Register DELETE routes: /v1/namespaces/{ns}/sandboxes/{sessionId}, /v1/namespaces/{ns}/sandboxes/name/{name}\n- [ ] **1.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/delete_options.go` - DeleteOptions struct with GracePeriodSeconds, Force, LabelSelector fields\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Graceful Shutdown\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-006/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775843859228,"end":1775843859246}}}}
