{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843920559,"sessionID":"ses_287754c6affeh2db39Jghf8MDv","part":{"id":"prt_d788b2a710013aDiC6sMMuu6cI","messageID":"msg_d788b126d001Hmlfcixq02JcY9","sessionID":"ses_287754c6affeh2db39Jghf8MDv","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_b8f2f5d3bee1452e82286913","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-006 — Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 Tasks\n\n**Module:** pkg/workloadmanager  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Complete)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Core Types & Error Definitions\n\n- [ ] **1.1** Add `DeleteOptions` struct to `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go` — fields: GracePeriodSeconds, Force, LabelSelector, Preconditions\n- [ ] **1.2** Add `ErrSandboxNotFound`, `ErrDeletionFailed`, `ErrStaleFinalizer`, `ErrOrphanedResource` to `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go`\n- [ ] **1.3** Add `WebhookConfig` struct to `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go` — fields: URL, Timeout, RetryCount\n- [ ] **1.4** Add `AuditLogEntry` struct to `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go` — fields: SandboxID, Namespace, Reason, Initiator, Duration, ResourcesCleaned\n- [ ] **1.5** Add `DeletionEvent` struct to `pkg/workloadmanager/types.go` — fields: Type, Reason, Message, InvolvedObject, Timestamp\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Deletion Handlers (HTTP Layer)\n\n- [ ] **2.1** Implement `handleDeleteSandbox` in `pkg/workloadmanager/server.go` — DELETE /api/v1/namespaces/{ns}/sandboxes/{sessionId}\n- [ ] **2.2** Add route registration for sandbox DELETE in server.go (existing agentruntime/codeinterpreter pattern)\n- [ ] **2.3** Implement query param binding for DeleteOptions (gracePeriodSeconds, force, labelSelector)\n- [ ] **2.4** Add HTTP 404 response for non-existent sandbox (AR-006-004)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: WorkloadManager Interface Extension\n\n- [ ] **3.1** Add `DeleteSandbox(ctx, namespace, sessionID string, opts DeleteOptions) error` to WorkloadManager interface\n- [ ] **3.2** Add `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, namespace, sessionID string) (*Sandbox, error)` to interface\n- [ ] **3.3** Add `ListSandboxes(ctx, namespace string, opts ListOptions) (*SandboxList, error)` to interface\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: Graceful Shutdown Implementation\n\n- [ ] **4.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/graceful.go` — implement `drainConnections(sandboxID)` to stop routing new traffic\n- [ ] **4.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/graceful.go` — implement `waitForConnections(sandboxID, timeout)` with context\n- [ ] **4.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/graceful.go` — implement `executePreDeleteHook(sandbox, hookConfig)` with timeout\n- [ ] **4.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/graceful.go` — implement `sendSIGTERM(podName, namespace)` via exec\n- [ ] **4.5** Integrate graceful shutdown into DeleteSandbox flow with gracePeriodSeconds support (AR-006-010)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: TTL & Expiration Logic\n\n- [ ] **5.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/expiration.go` — implement `isExpiredByTTL(sandbox)` check\n- [ ] **5.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/expiration.go` — implement `isExpiredByIdleTimeout(sandbox)` check\n- [ ] **5.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/expiration.go` — implement `isExpiredByMaxLifetime(sandbox)` check\n- [ ] **5.4** Add DefaultTTL, DefaultIdleTimeout, DefaultMaxLifetime constants to `pkg/workloadmanager/defaults.go`\n- [ ] **5.5** Implement expiration check in garbage collector loop (AR-006-020, AR-006-021, AR-006-022)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 6: Batch Deletion Operations\n\n- [ ] **6.1** Implement `handleDeleteAllSandboxes` — DELETE /api/v1/namespaces/{ns}/sandboxes?deleteAll=true\n- [ ] **6.2** Implement `handleDeleteByLabelSelector` — DELETE with labelSelector query param\n- [ ] **6.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/batch.go` — implement `deleteStaleSandboxes()` for Unknown/Failed state > 1hr\n- [ ] **6.4** Add async deletion support for batch operations > 10 sandboxes\n\n---\n\n## Phase 7: Resource Cleanup\n\n- [ ] **7.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/cleanup.go` — implement `cleanupServices(namespace, ownerRef)` using ownerReference\n- [ ] **7.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/cleanup.go` — implement `cleanupConfigMaps(namespace, ownerRef)` with deletion标记\n- [ ] **7.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/cleanup.go` — implement `cleanupPVCs(namespace, ownerRef)` respecting ReclaimPolicy\n- [ ] **7.4** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/cleanup.go` — implement `cleanupOrphanedResources(sandbox)` for AR-006-061\n\n---\n\n## Phase 8: Lifecycle Events & Webhooks\n\n- [ ] **8.1** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/events.go` — implement `emitDeletionEvent(sandbox, reason)` using k8s event recorder\n- [ ] **8.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/events.go` — implement `sendDeletionWebhook(sandbox, config)` with retry (max 3)\n- [ ] **8.3** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/events.go` — implement `logDeletionAudit(entry)` for audit trail\n- [ ] **8.4** Integrate events into DeleteSandbox flow\n\n---\n\n## Phase 9: Error Handling & Retry\n\n- [ ] **9.1** Map new error types to HTTP status codes in `server.go` handleError method\n- [ ] **9.2** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/retry.go` — implement `retryDeletion(ctx, fn, maxRetries)` with exponential backoff\n- [ ] **9.3** Add retry logic to garbage collector for transient deletion failures\n\n---\n\n## Phase 10: Integration with AR-005\n\n- [ ] **10.1** Hook into sandbox creation failure path — call cleanup on rollback\n- [ ] **10.2** Use existing k8s_client from AR-005 for all deletion operations\n- [ ] **10.3** Integrate with informer watches for sandbox state tracking\n- [ ] **10.4** Reuse store's DeleteSandbox/GetSandbox methods\n\n---\n\n## Phase 11: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **11.1** `pkg/workloadmanager/delete_test.go` — TestDeleteSandbox_Success (AR-006-001)\n- [ ] **11.2** `pkg/workloadmanager/delete_test.go` — TestDeleteSandbox_NotFound (AR-006-004)\n- [ ] **11.3** `pkg/workloadmanager/delete_test.go` — TestDeleteSandbox_ForceDelete (AR-006-003)\n- [ ] **11.4** `pkg/workloadmanager/graceful_test.go` — TestDrainConnections (AR-006-012)\n- [ ] **11.5** `pkg/workloadmanager/graceful_test.go` — TestExecutePreDeleteHook (AR-006-011)\n- [ ] **11.6** `pkg/workloadmanager/expiration_test.go` — TestIsExpired_TTL (AR-006-020)\n- [ ] **11.7** `pkg/workloadmanager/expiration_test.go` — TestIsExpired_IdleTimeout (AR-006-021)\n- [ ] **11.8** `pkg/workloadmanager/batch_test.go` — TestDeleteAllInNamespace (AR-006-030)\n- [ ] **11.9** `pkg/workloadmanager/batch_test.go` — TestDeleteByLabelSelector (AR-006-031)\n- [ ] **11.10** `pkg/workloadmanager/events_test.go` — TestEmitDeletionEvent (AR-006-040)\n- [ ] **11.11** `pkg/workloadmanager/cleanup_test.go` — TestCleanupServices (AR-006-050)\n- [ ] **11.12** `pkg/workloadmanager/cleanup_test.go` — TestCleanupPVCs_RetainPolicy (AR-006-052)\n\n---\n\n## Phase 12: Integration Tests\n\n- [ ] **12.1** `pkg/workloadmanager/e2e_delete_test.go` — E2E sandbox deletion flow\n- [ ] **12.2** E2E graceful shutdown with active connections\n- [ ] **12.3** E2E TTL expiration and auto-cleanup\n- [ ] **12.4** E2E batch deletion with 100+ sandboxes\n\n---\n\n## Phase 13: Verification\n\n- [ ] **13.1** `go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` — successful compilation\n- [ ] **13.2** `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` — all unit tests pass\n- [ ] **13.3** `go test -race ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` — no race conditions\n- [ ] **13.4** `go vet ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` — no issues\n- [ ] **13.5** `golangci-lint run ./pkg/workloadmanager/...` — linter passes\n- [ ] **13.6** Test coverage > 40% (`go test -coverprofile=c.out ./pkg/workloadmanager/...`)\n\n---\n\n## Dependency Graph\n\n| Task | Depends On |\n|------|------------|\n| Phase 1 | — (standalone) |\n| Phase 2 | Phase 1, Phase 3 |\n| Phase 3 | Phase 1 |\n| Phase 4 | Phase 2 |\n| Phase 5 | Phase 1 |\n| Phase 6 | Phase 2, Phase 3 |\n| Phase 7 | AR-005 (k8s_client) |\n| Phase 8 | Phase 1 |\n| Phase 9 | Phase 1, Phase 2 |\n| Phase 10 | AR-005 complete |\n| Phase 11 | Phase 1-10 |\n| Phase 12 | Phase 11 |\n| Phase 13 | Phase 11-12 |\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Delta Spec: `changes/AR-006/delta-spec.md`\n- Design: ST-3 completed\n- Related AR: AR-005 (Sandbox 创建处理器)","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-006/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/client/informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go\">\nERROR [4:2] \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\" imported and not used\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/workloadmanager/server_test.go\">\nERROR [15:2] \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/watch\" imported and not used\nERROR [66:14] cannot use &metav1.Status{…} (value of type *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status) as error value in return statement: *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status does not implement error (missing method Error)\nERROR [81:9] cannot use &metav1.Status{…} (value of type *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status) as error value in return statement: *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status does not implement error (missing method Error)\nERROR [95:14] cannot use &metav1.Status{…} (value of type *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status) as error value in return statement: *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status does not implement error (missing method Error)\nERROR [109:14] cannot use &metav1.Status{…} (value of type *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status) as error value in return statement: *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status does not implement error (missing method Error)\nERROR [132:14] cannot use &metav1.Status{…} (value of type *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\".Status) as error value in return statement: *\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"